  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sacrifice game from one Arab developer. In this game, you enter a suspicious island to do your job and solve puzzles and try to discover the secrets of the mysterious island. Enjoy and good luck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What you need to do</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover the island and the fate of those who were on it</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solve puzzles to advance the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-The difficulty of the puzzle depends on your intelligence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck and have a fun!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sacrifice game from one Arab developer. In this game, you enter a suspicious island to do your job and solve puzzles and try to discover the secrets of the mysterious island. Enjoy and good luck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What you need to do</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover the island and the fate of those who were on it</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solve puzzles to advance the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-The difficulty of the puzzle depends on your intelligence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck and have a fun!</p></li></ul>",
